{"tid":2264308,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北區物語●花光積蓄粉嶺開黃店  警總飯堂前經理：能伸張正義是回報","createTime":"2020-10-30T14:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T14:37:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4956d5850cf28048f564989df96731f24770fc8e","tid":2264308,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20201030/IROYGTEQNFDN5OIDE53PBBSSNI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20201030%2FIROYGTEQNFDN5OIDE53PBBSSNI%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdg%2BoCD4UrwaevtQIqI6x5z0%3D&h=594e834d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20201030%2FIROYGTEQNFDN5OIDE53PBBSSNI%2F&h=7280ddb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20201030/IROYGTEQNFDN5OIDE53PBBSSNI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n北區物語●花光積蓄粉嶺開黃店 <br />\n警總飯堂前經理：能伸張正義是回報<br />\n<br />\n記者 : 王秋婷<br />\n<br />\n去年6.12那天，仍在灣仔警察總部飯堂當經理的徐逸昇（Ricky）跟許多香港人一樣，被電視直播的槍聲與催淚彈撼動心臟，翌日二話不說就回公司扔下辭職信，加入黑壓壓的遊行隊伍。無業一年收入歸零，試過參選區議會，試過做助選義工，盼在運動中尋找適合自己的角色。最後決定回歸老本行，返回社區開黃店賣川味米線，並把它命名為琭玥玖，以紀念去年6.9，把香港人命運連在一起的那一天。<br />\n<br />\n很多人光顧琭玥玖，也未必一眼認出Ricky，因為他總是站在廚房，背對着客人，默默準備食材、醃製肉類、調製醬汁，有時一企就企幾個鐘。他既是老闆，亦是每天親自落場的主廚。<br />\n<br />\n這一年，。。。。。。。。。。。。，「去年六月尾七月頭在網上見到有『反自動當選運動』我就參與了，選舉時發現自己撞了區，就退出讓同區的呂智恆選。」Ricky明白自己未必適合從政，但已站了出來，猶如「洗濕咗個頭」，總要繼續走下去。<br />\n<br />\n「我們考慮過這時勢開店是否不太好，二月時開始睇舖，港九新界都看過，因為粉嶺區少黃店，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jIN8-7kWK6u3NIXsRf1YzGRlASM=/6000x3376/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KZP5WZNXIFCHRKCDF5DNZE6NAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjIN8-7kWK6u3NIXsRf1YzGRlASM%3D%2F6000x3376%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKZP5WZNXIFCHRKCDF5DNZE6NAI.jpg&h=cc345a9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警總前飯堂經理Ricky在粉嶺開黃店琭玥玖，紀念去年6.9反送中大遊行，也為港人的味蕾提供多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pHmb-Lu78XpgI-PfalkFBx6UGPw=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EN4C6CHV7ZHUHJFCSYCCRVBIWE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpHmb-Lu78XpgI-PfalkFBx6UGPw%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEN4C6CHV7ZHUHJFCSYCCRVBIWE.jpg&h=ce88b1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRicky希望參考車仔麵檔的模式，將煮餐過程簡化，讓新手員工容易上手。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/h7vpibbUoafjmclKb6DvTIiFIp8=/5297x2980/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N2URUXFOOZFMLH52HA3IUGPNYE.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh7vpibbUoafjmclKb6DvTIiFIp8%3D%2F5297x2980%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN2URUXFOOZFMLH52HA3IUGPNYE.JPG&h=b5b16894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞絲粉皮$22：以獨門川味醬汁調味的花生醬是精華所在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B3rzT2F25264YpL3J4OPx8PXqRk=/5352x3011/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RG5RARGMRFGYRBOROCQQB7KZHY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB3rzT2F25264YpL3J4OPx8PXqRk%3D%2F5352x3011%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRG5RARGMRFGYRBOROCQQB7KZHY.JPG&h=c69919f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水煮魚米線$58：每早6時開始煮湯底，以雞殼和豬骨熬5小時。水煮魚以花椒粒、指天椒、野生椒、燈籠椒及四川香料醃製。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9Ly-Zsno7RHnGaQLXzbXIxFpSPs=/6000x3376/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XNGC42TV2VBHHAILP3R3VZMXMU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9Ly-Zsno7RHnGaQLXzbXIxFpSPs%3D%2F6000x3376%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXNGC42TV2VBHHAILP3R3VZMXMU.JPG&h=a8398d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鎮江餚肉$28：入口即融齒頰留香，由Ricky的師傅每周親手製作，以平民價吃到米芝蓮水準。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Cc0R5FAufEnEcX38l1e-lGWgdAU=/5917x3329/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YAKE7VUALREMLNPOKEMSBCSNOU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCc0R5FAufEnEcX38l1e-lGWgdAU%3D%2F5917x3329%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYAKE7VUALREMLNPOKEMSBCSNOU.JPG&h=e2af3fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n口水雞$40：雞腿嫩滑厚肉，先以紹興酒、香料、薑葱及鹽浸雞調味，再加上秘製辣汁，非常滋味。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高調堅定表態：政權難封閉思想<br />\n<br />\n從警總辭職後，Ricky大半年沒有收入，靠全力支持自己的太太撐起家庭。投資七十萬元開店，Ricky笑言早花光了積蓄。「搵舖過程遇到不少困難，最後以大約二至三萬元月租，在粉嶺花都開店，這邊是偏僻民生區，未必有外區人進來，所以主打街坊生意。」近。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n烹飪經驗欠奉的Ricky之前曾在四川菜餐廳工作，與川菜廚師關係好，所以開琭玥玖前他專程去拜師學藝，師傅是來自米芝蓮一星餐廳的高手。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n小店主打川味米線和小食。水煮魚米線是店中招牌，米線湯底每早六時開始煮，。。。。。。。。。。。。。頰留香，由Ricky的師傅每周親手製作，可算是以平民價就吃到米芝蓮水準的豐腴滋味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u5KlC6lHO-VKFF4mOUy31UVH0-E=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CLFPI4KRAFEY7M5X7ZJJDJE5CM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu5KlC6lHO-VKFF4mOUy31UVH0-E%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCLFPI4KRAFEY7M5X7ZJJDJE5CM.jpg&h=25ac8c6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琭玥玖一天大約賣200碗米線，怕熱的Ricky一天花13小時在廚房處理食材。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/r3Dj60zS82B_BBuqFPQ3RNDhWwg=/1216x1140/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UK4QSAEBCJDUPAKM755MH7CHVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fr3Dj60zS82B_BBuqFPQ3RNDhWwg%3D%2F1216x1140%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUK4QSAEBCJDUPAKM755MH7CHVY.jpg&h=d5797521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n八月初，琭玥玖開店不久，附近街坊就蜂擁而至。琭玥玖fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n犧牲自己頭家 保護香港這個家<br />\n<br />\n然而疫情慘淡氛圍下開黃店，是打大佬的級數。Ricky最大的犧牲，是跟妻女的相處時間。為了做好小店，Ricky說私人時間已再也不重要，即使女兒成長中有那麼一段日子，周一至周五飯桌上爸爸總是缺席，一個同一屋簷下每天見面的家庭，忽爾相隔了二十二公里的距離，「我和太太暫時分開居住，兩個女兒跟她搬了去外家那邊住，在大圍上學；小朋友由媽媽照顧，我要顧舖頭則留在粉嶺獨居，暫時一周只能見一次。」<br />\n<br />\n分隔一周後每次的小團圓，Ricky一回家女兒就飛身抱着爸爸，「做飲食業很難收早或放到周六日陪家人，警總工作時間穩定返八放四，收入二萬多元，就是這個原因吸引我去做，配合到我照顧女兒的時間，是當時重要考慮因素。」二〇一四年傘運後Ricky心灰意冷，一心想先照顧好女兒，先做隻港豬算了，掙扎過後，還是進了警總。然而這一次，他無法再視而不見，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qvvThAiKHjZdFIuFMHZnEa81WJc=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNA2K6HE2BE53ATYCPUZ74MQKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqvvThAiKHjZdFIuFMHZnEa81WJc%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNA2K6HE2BE53ATYCPUZ74MQKU.jpg&h=68fe86ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店仔細細裝潢簡單，沒有多餘的裝飾，賣平民價食物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QsOoamMzg9wDpDynBazwKwC-Mb8=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RSQWH54BSRGX7ONB6KWH2DOLUA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQsOoamMzg9wDpDynBazwKwC-Mb8%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRSQWH54BSRGX7ONB6KWH2DOLUA.jpg&h=512be8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRicky望着掛在警總那張「如果你想保護香港這個家」的巨型海報，有種說不出口的荒誕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n琭玥玖<br />\n粉嶺花都商場地下9號舖<br />\n<br />\n記者：王秋婷<br />\n<br />\n攝影：郭于祺、伍永健"},{"pid":"072ed85961cda880cdf558b635a96d7cf5c4a7bd","tid"